Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.04,0:00:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cue!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.21,0:00:20.41,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,424)\fade(1000,0)}Etsuko Yamanobe
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.85,0:00:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening. This is News Flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.72,0:00:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Top story this evening is the latest on the hostage crisis...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.22,0:00:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that occurred earlier today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.72,0:00:29.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A man holding a sharp object\Nbroke into an apartment building...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.36,0:00:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...in Suginami ward this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.59,0:00:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's still holding a young woman as a hostage...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.70,0:00:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and has been inside ever since this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.13,0:00:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He shouts out gibberish at times.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.83,0:00:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm from Venus!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.84,0:00:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm telling you to get my boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.97,0:00:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l have some business with her father!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.44,0:00:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't do anything stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.21,0:00:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.51,0:00:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.45,0:00:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l was fired from my job today!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.92,0:00:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.79,0:00:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The female hostage is believed to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.99,0:01:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...22-year-old Mayumi Wakabayashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.13,0:01:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l want you to hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.96,0:01:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lose hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.14,0:01:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This just in...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.90,0:01:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The suspect is believed to be 40-\Nyear-old Damesuke Marude who...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.74,0:01:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was fired today from a company\Nowned by the victim's father.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.79,0:01:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Fujiwara, it seems the suspect\Nwas irate over his recent firing...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.33,0:01:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and has taken the daughter of\Nhis former boss to get even.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.00,0:01:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.50,0:01:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's a typical crime that occurs\Nin this age of economic depression.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.30,0:01:51.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We now know the reason behind this crime...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.04,0:01:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but we can say that the\Ngovernment doesn't care about...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.74,0:01:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the lives of ordinary people and\Nrealize what's going on in society.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.01,0:01:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.28,0:02:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Fujiwara...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.52,0:02:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'd like to head over to the scene and\Ntry to negotiate with the suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.59,0:02:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.39,0:02:11.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll say this to the suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.16,0:02:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you watching this broadcast?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.19,0:02:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop resisting and surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.80,0:02:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's foolish for you to keep doing this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.64,0:02:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm Etsuko Yamanobe from Tokyo Flower TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.61,0:02:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm heading over there right\Nnow, so please let me talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.85,0:02:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Yamanobe, you gave\Nquite a show for the audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.95,0:02:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.02,0:02:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l was just excited by my indignation\Ntowards social evils.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.82,0:02:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just what l expected to\Nhear from our popular newscaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.73,0:02:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.43,0:02:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, about the cameraman who will go with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.60,0:02:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you get me Matsuura?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.80,0:02:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuura?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.37,0:02:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's just a newbie.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.07,0:02:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.34,0:02:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to train him at the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.84,0:03:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say, strike while the iron is hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.84,0:03:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l have to stop by someplace, so\Ntell him to meet me at the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.79,0:03:18.49,title,,0000,0000,0000,,Foxy Nudes Vol. 1
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.42,0:03:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm Miyata from the headquarters\Nof Armed Security Pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.89,0:03:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm Etsuko Yamanobe from Flower TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.60,0:04:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for choosing us over\Nother security companies out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.87,0:04:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have solved many cases\Ninvolving hostages in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.08,0:04:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we're used to cases like this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.55,0:04:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have done our research\Nthoroughly and we already...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.65,0:04:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...gathered details regarding the\Nsuspect and the hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.23,0:04:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The suspect is 40-year-old Damesuke Marude.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.23,0:04:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has a history of alcohol abuse...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.86,0:04:30.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and has received treatment in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.30,0:04:33.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's introverted, but can easily fly into a rage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.90,0:04:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We believe he's in an excited state right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.11,0:04:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The victim is 22-year-old\NMayumi Wakabayashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.41,0:04:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the daughter of Genta Wakabayashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...who is the president\Nof Wakabayashi lncorporated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.12,0:04:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not related to the suspect at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.32,0:04:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her sizes are 88, 56, 89, she's been\Ninvolved with five men in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.49,0:05:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what do you plan on doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.56,0:05:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm going to block the area nearby...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.53,0:05:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and we'll provide support\Nfor your negotiating plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.04,0:05:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we'll bust right in if we feel you're in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.37,0:05:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll safely rescue the hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.71,0:05:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.64,0:05:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about in case of emergency?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.65,0:05:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ln case of emergency?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be optional, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can snipe the suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.72,0:05:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.72,0:05:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l want to give the audience the entire\Nstory and get really high ratings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.86,0:05:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.80,0:05:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf l can't accomplish that,\Nthen l can't work with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.87,0:05:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.32,0:05:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Etsuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.72,0:06:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't even answer her cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.73,0:06:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir! l'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.06,0:06:11.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The contract was inside my bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.97,0:06:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When l was about to leave the office...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.37,0:06:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.68,0:06:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.92,0:06:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you waiting for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.65,0:06:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to talk to him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.29,0:06:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.09,0:06:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up Murata.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.88,0:06:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.85,0:07:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm sorry, l'll go back and get a new copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.78,0:07:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.19,0:07:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.39,0:07:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.25,0:07:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're settling the accounts pretty soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.35,0:07:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd like to pay the regular\Nfee and get the option for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.29,0:07:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we'll be criticized by the\Npeople if we use the sniper method...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.50,0:07:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.70,0:07:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what l need is a partner\Nthat can accomplish the task.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.12,0:08:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So l want you to use the sniper method.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to lower the price\Nand use the sniper method?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.06,0:08:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're asking too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.60,0:08:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the hostage will be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.87,0:08:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your company will gain popularity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.80,0:08:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.60,0:08:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's something you can gain\Nby working with our TV station.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.84,0:08:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's a simple give and take process.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.65,0:08:42.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf you do what l say,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.48,0:08:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll personally pay you the money\Nfor the next ten jobs...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.35,0:08:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...without signing any contracts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.89,0:08:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.29,0:08:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll do my best so we can be great partners.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.16,0:08:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.50,0:09:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it Murata?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.04,0:09:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm in the middle of an important business negotiation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.77,0:09:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Business negotiation? Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.41,0:09:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's a good way of negotiating business.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.72,0:09:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.19,0:09:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ln this crazy world where we have\Nto protect ourselves from harm...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.92,0:09:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know why your company...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.56,0:09:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...stands out from rest of the security firms?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.93,0:09:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.84,0:11:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Send the contract to the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.22,0:11:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you planning to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.29,0:11:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.29,0:11:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You found out about our secret treaty.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.52,0:11:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.83,0:11:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you keep the secret to yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.43,0:11:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you'll be in a favorable position.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.30,0:11:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.47,0:11:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is your wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.04,0:11:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for what you truly want.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.01,0:11:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the way to live life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.02,0:12:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll kill myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.36,0:12:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll definitely kill myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.59,0:12:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But before l do...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.83,0:12:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'll kill you with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.76,0:12:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Mayumi, can you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.03,0:12:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.57,0:12:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Marude!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.70,0:12:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l didn't know you were this dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.24,0:12:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give us back our daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.97,0:12:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You rotten bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.34,0:12:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.51,0:12:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You ruined my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.91,0:12:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because you were incompetent!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.88,0:12:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You went to collect money...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.81,0:12:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but instead they collected money from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.58,0:12:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You worthless piece of crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.62,0:12:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.72,0:12:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.65,0:12:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father, mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were never like this, Damesuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.96,0:12:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He should've never worked for\Na bogus company like yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a very timid boy, so\Nyou took advantage of him...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.73,0:12:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.03,0:12:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He should be grateful for\Nhaving a job in this day and age!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.54,0:12:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you thank us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.57,0:12:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're messing with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.82,0:13:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attention people of the\Nnews media and bystanders...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.09,0:13:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This case will be handled by Armed Security Pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.33,0:13:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, this hostage crisis will be\Nbroadcast live by Tokyo Flower TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.96,0:13:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? We're doing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.27,0:13:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other news media and bystanders\Nshould follow directions from our...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.87,0:13:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... officers and leave this area immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.52,0:13:44.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus we'll be choosing 100 random bystanders...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.05,0:13:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to join us in our special seats.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.35,0:13:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For more details, please ask one of our officers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.20,0:13:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not a show!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.33,0:14:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come this way please.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.37,0:14:05.81,sign,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Parents of suspect, Parents of hostage{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.94,0:14:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wouldn't do anything like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.21,0:14:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.22,0:14:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuura!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.15,0:14:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry l'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.95,0:14:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Etsuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.55,0:14:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.23,0:14:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Yamanobe from Tokyo Flower TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.90,0:14:30.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is my cameraman.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.33,0:14:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your assistance!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.34,0:14:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.14,0:14:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.54,0:14:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead, you have to get rid of your grudge.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.47,0:14:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.91,0:14:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that's our channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.28,0:14:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you possibly be...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.32,0:14:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm newscaster Etsuko Yamanobe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.25,0:14:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf you were watching the news,\Nthen you know why l'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.19,0:14:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l said l wanted to negotiate with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.06,0:14:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up you bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.10,0:15:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm a fifth degree black belt in karate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.20,0:15:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't beat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.54,0:15:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm saved...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.59,0:15:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.52,0:15:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l want you to take your clothes off.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.12,0:15:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.89,0:15:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.19,0:15:31.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l want you to do it according to my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.93,0:15:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.90,0:15:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to be a star?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.30,0:15:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.27,0:15:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than depending on your parents' money...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.67,0:15:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...why don't you think about\Nmaking your own money?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.64,0:15:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your parents squeezed money from the weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.21,0:15:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so their money is filled with their hatred.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by ''a star''?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.71,0:15:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You play the pitiable victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.52,0:15:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just have to overact by crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.15,0:16:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be quiet after a good beating.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.72,0:16:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.22,0:16:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After you're rescued, you'll sign a\Ncontract with us and appear on TV...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.23,0:16:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...then you'll be writing a book about your tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.83,0:16:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course a ghostwriter will write\Nit, you have nothing to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.60,0:16:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The more pitiful you are the\Nmore collateral money you'll get.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.91,0:16:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So your clothes have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.09,0:16:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l heard from your boss that you're worthless scum.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.86,0:16:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But l don't think you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.63,0:16:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.40,0:16:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, l want you to attack her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l want to capture a shocking scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.15,0:17:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuura!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.15,0:17:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you naked?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.15,0:17:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huge story!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.19,0:17:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.42,0:17:10.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.89,0:17:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Start the camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.96,0:17:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.40,0:17:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, don't come any closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.40,0:17:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.31,0:17:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.01,0:17:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.42,0:17:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.82,0:17:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.58,0:17:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up you bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.62,0:17:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.70,0:17:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.70,0:17:51.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.49,0:18:21.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.73,0:18:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me that when we're alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.27,0:18:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes Mr. Miyata.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.40,0:18:57.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is Miyata...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.90,0:19:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? The suspect?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.50,0:19:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.70,0:19:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf he's doing that, then l can't negotiate with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.14,0:19:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The suspect is trying to kill himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.98,0:19:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf he climaxes, then he probably won't need her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.85,0:19:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's reached the limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.39,0:19:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But l'll try to keep him busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.59,0:19:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l want you to carry out the\Nsniper option as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.72,0:20:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Murata.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.99,0:20:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Mr. Miyata?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.19,0:20:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're working, address me properly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.59,0:20:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.06,0:20:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you go to the crime scene with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.46,0:20:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.13,0:20:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're short of officers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.60,0:20:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The strike team will carry out the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.97,0:20:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be recorded in our records as\Nbeing part of the special unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.54,0:20:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.68,0:20:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.78,0:20:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After this case is solved...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.38,0:20:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you'll receive a special allowance and an award.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.49,0:21:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus you'll get a position as an important secretary!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.05,0:21:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.86,0:21:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take that you old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.10,0:21:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You like what l'm doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.90,0:21:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damesuke Marude is really no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.30,0:21:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.17,0:21:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you completely satisfied by doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.67,0:21:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you take her as a hostage?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.88,0:21:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.54,0:21:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lf l don't show this to that\Nold man, there's really no point.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.28,0:21:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Matsuura.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.38,0:21:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.32,0:21:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l want you to start shooting this live.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.20,0:21:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l wonder if Etsuko Yamanobe's show is still on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.34,0:21:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The suspect has appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.87,0:21:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.12,0:22:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.62,0:22:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's definitely scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.22,0:22:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, you don't have to shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.16,0:22:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You just let the others do the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.24,0:22:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.28,0:22:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.10,0:22:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.20,0:22:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you people do anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.14,0:22:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.47,0:23:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.38,0:23:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The suspect brought the victim out on the balcony...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.64,0:23:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and he is raping her before the public's eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.75,0:23:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l'm Yamanobe from Tokyo Flower\NTV, and just like l stated earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.19,0:23:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...l came here to the scene of the\Ncrime to negotiate with the suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.76,0:23:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But sadly, negotiations have failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.56,0:23:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this is where we stand right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.57,0:23:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Etsuko Yamanobe...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.47,0:23:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Etsuko Yamanobe...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.10,0:23:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By reporting from this scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.94,0:23:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l hope that you viewers can see\Nand feel angry towards the suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.08,0:23:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take a look at what's happening now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.35,0:23:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you all see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.92,0:23:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.62,0:23:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's an amazing blowjob!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.62,0:23:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unbelievable...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.13,0:23:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We feel that it's dangerous, but we can't escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.70,0:23:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can anyone do something about this situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.35,0:24:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a really good urinal.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.65,0:24:23.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l don't know what to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.89,0:24:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it feels good to urinate in someone's mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.79,0:24:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,l know how it feels since l do it sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.26,0:24:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She pisses in other people's mouths?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.00,0:25:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.93,0:25:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.98,0:25:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.12,0:25:26.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is terrible! lt's getting worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.25,0:25:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is going to happen from here on?